{"tid":1583513,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"建議各位唔好濟睇熱門 睇下時事同政事台","createTime":"2019-09-20T15:41:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T15:48:02.000Z","uid":129529,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d2efb627118236cbc23157f010b7eb0640dd64c4","tid":1583513,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"熱門太多膠post同非行動post  會miss左好多野"},{"pid":"8352e1e685d250681af001e4457917610ee7cd72","tid":1583513,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:41:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a47041628f48245f74e2193233e1fecb0abd126c","tid":1583513,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a85bcba4afed0492b556901c8313312cf71bf144","tid":1583513,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:42:19.000Z","msg":"開錯台"},{"pid":"8371f90293377a86454415936f251e9134dcb682","tid":1583513,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:42:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f8f454a4ba2de5e64c32169cf6c799cda2fc00d","tid":1583513,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:42:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28c559066a2375f9ab115678ed36a9e9f3a01450","tid":1583513,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:42:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcb784b195bd142ac17c105bd4fb45c07284ac72","tid":1583513,"uid":8075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"我嘅做法係自選台set凈時事同政事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5bc2faf86e7cd2f2e31b602d426efee5139546","tid":1583513,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:43:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54cc38505ffff8fea8b15bb7dc3fe3ee25e2a3ef","tid":1583513,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府</span></span>借減碳排放為名，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要向中國買電</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」詻詢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日截止</span></span><br />\n快啲將你既意見SEND EMAIL去：  comments@susdev.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n✏參考意見✏<br />\n<br />\n致可持續發展委員會成員：<br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」諮詢中，當局建議以「 更緊密的區域合作」向中國購買零排放電力，然而本港電力穩定度遠高於中國南方電網，擔心向中國買電會帶來電力不穩，影響本港金融、航運、交通、以至市民日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n此外，《巴黎協定》為一些面積小、欠缺天然資源的小島嶼發展中國家(Small Island Developing States,SIDS) 如新加坡、斐濟等，可因應它們特殊情況，制訂關於溫室氣體低排放發展的策略。<br />\n由於香港地少人多，局限可再生能源發展，亦缺乏天然資源，可選擇的減排策略有限，與其他小島嶼發展中國家情況面臨同樣的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n就此本人有以下意見：<br />\n<br />\n一. 聯網供電會損害供電穩定，故此反對進一步向中國買電，反對採取更緊密的區域合作，香港應以本地發電為主，確保電力穩定；<br />\n二. 遵照2014年未來發電燃料組合諮詢，增加本地天然氣發電及可再生能源比例，代替區域聯網；<br />\n三. 爭取香港以地區名義，直接向政府間氣候變化專門委員會(IPCC)匯報減排策略；<br />\n四. 爭取以發展中國家/地區(Small Island Developing States) 名義，因應香港的情況，以更彈性的方式履行《巴黎協定》；<br />\n五. 放緩人口增長，收緊移民政策，減低整體耗電量；<br />\n六. 制訂具體香港再工業化政策，加強本港農業及回收業的支援，減少貨物入口時的碳排放。"},{"pid":"4b504084530ae6314c781247d12222dd34258b1c","tid":1583513,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcb784b195bd142ac17c105bd4fb45c07284ac72","tid":1583513,"uid":8075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"我嘅做法係自選台set凈時事同政事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"各位參考一下"},{"pid":"be9056667ed0667bfe510e71c463e3be343850d7","tid":1583513,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b504084530ae6314c781247d12222dd34258b1c","tid":1583513,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcb784b195bd142ac17c105bd4fb45c07284ac72","tid":1583513,"uid":8075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"我嘅做法係自選台set凈時事同政事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"各位參考一下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:43:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03800cf66a43a66ad4a99c5a9738be6d8ea4dbe1","tid":1583513,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:43:49.000Z","msg":"不嬲唔睇熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d5145d47b2f7cc7b4917987e0b85c2fa7c65ea","tid":1583513,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:43:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc9386dfc265244fdfe8181ff2447200743ddb45","tid":1583513,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:44:47.000Z","msg":"自選台"},{"pid":"d1c96548caa94a1980f1290016b42d49bb3f010e","tid":1583513,"uid":8075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:47:14.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"1275ec0262de14968e78364994f94891461a30bc","tid":1583513,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:48:02.000Z","msg":"推"}]}